e group struggled to promote and the members had different ideas of what type of music they should be releasing. So, in January 2021, Kithewhale Entertainment announced the group's disbandment. Four members remained with the company but he decided to leave.\n\nAfter switching agencies, he re-debuted in July 2021 (under the stage name Hyuk) as a member of OMEGA X with their first single album, \"Vamos\". However, in October 2022, a video of the CEO of OMEGA X's label (Spire Entertainment) abusing him and his group members came to light. The members filed a lawsuit against their company to cancel their exclusive contracts and to file for the trademark of their group name. In January 2023, OMEGA X won the lawsuit and officially ended their contract with the agency. This was finally made official on May 8, 2023. The group is has been represented by IPQ since July 2023.","name":"Yang Hyuk","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"양혁","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"梁爀（양혁，Yang Hyuk），藝名為爀（혁，Hyuk）為韓國男子團體OMEGA X（오메가엑스）的一員。","name":"梁爀","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"梁爀（양혁，Yang Hyuk），藝名為爀（혁，Hyuk）為韓國男子團體 OMEGA X（오메가엑스）的一員。","name":"梁爀","primary":false}}]}},"person_1266002_translations":{"at":1772689464251,"data":{"id":1266002,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Yohanes Roosyanto Landung Laksono Simatupang is an Indonesian actor. He started acting on the drama stage and his first appearance in the film is in Daun di Atas Pillow (1998).","name":"Landung Simatupang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ID","iso_639_1":"id","name":"Bahasa indonesia","english_name":"Indonesian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Landung Simatupang","primary":true}}]}},"tv_260471_detai