츠시타 나오","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nao Macušita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HU","iso_639_1":"hu","name":"Magyar","english_name":"Hungarian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Macusita Nao","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"ml","name":"","english_name":"Malayalam","data":{"biography":"","name":"നാവോ മത്സുഷിറ്റ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"نائو ماتسوشیتا","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FI","iso_639_1":"fi","name":"suomi","english_name":"Finnish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nao Matsushita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"NL","iso_639_1":"nl","name":"Nederlands","english_name":"Dutch","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nao Matsushita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"ناو ماتسوشيتا","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AL","iso_639_1":"sq","name":"shqip","english_name":"Albanian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nao Matsushita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Нао Мацусита","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nao Matsushita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nao Matsushita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ID","iso_639_1":"id","name":"Bahasa indonesia","english_name":"Indonesian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nao Matsushita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IE","iso_639_1":"ga","name":"Gaeilge","english_name":"Irish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nao Matsushita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"松下奈緖，日本女演員。她在 2006 年以作曲家與鋼琴家身份，發行出道專輯！3 歲開始學習鋼琴。2006 年在演出聯續劇與電影忙碌行程當中，松下奈緖每一首曲子都認真誠摯地投入，專輯也收錄了松下創作的 2 首曲子，體驗出她的作曲才華。而代表日本參賽 2006 年亞太影展的電影【鐵線厥的憂鬱】(Adiandum Blue) 則是松下奈緖首度參與電影演出，她擔任女主角葉子，電影以法國尼斯為舞台，與人氣不墜的演員阿部寬有精彩對手戲演出。松下奈緖演奏片中 3 首電影組曲，由活躍於日本電影, 日劇, 廣告配樂的作曲家大島 MICHIRU 編寫 (代表作有：《鋼之鍊金術師》、電影《失樂園》、《模仿犯》等)，像是沉浸在「旅遊歐洲，觀賞歐洲」的氣氛。松下的鋼琴演奏有著獨特風格，自然不做作的氣息，宛如輕聲慢語，令人心情沈穩安和。","name":"松下奈緖","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Нао Мацушіта","primary":false}}]}}}}